				<div class="uk-text page-heading uk-text-large uk-text-capitalize uk-margin-large-left splash-burgundy splash-charter section-title">Primary</div>
				<div class="page-hero" style="background-image: url(images/IMG_0874-min.jpg)"></div>

				<div class="intro-section-container spring-wood-bg">
					<div class="intro-text-container uk-padding mobile-padding">
						<div class=" uk-text uk-text-left">
							<h3 class="uk-text-left column-title"><span>Welcome Message from the Primary </span></h3>
							<p class="uk-margin-top text-body">
								The most informative years of an individual is their primary years. With minds like a sponge to grasp everts bit of information, tangible and intangible, we make sure to curb their minds in the best manner, academically and via their character and behaviour. 
							</p>

						</div>


					</div>
					<div class="uk-text bg-intro-text uk-text-large uk-text-capitalize muted-page-title splash-white">Primary</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<!--/SCHOOL INTRODUCTION-->
