			<section class="uk-section section-width mobile-padding-remove">
				<div class=" uk-text">
					<div class="uk-text-left splash-burgundy splash-charter section-title"><span>Academic Programme & Curriculum</span></div>
				</div>
				<div class=" uk-text">
					<p class="uk-margin-top text-body">
						The curriculum is designed to enhance the development of academic, social, emotional, creative and physical skills with respect to the Ghana Education Service(GES). Children are encouraged to pursue excellence, whilst being challenged at their own level of development.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
